---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Business & IT Consulting | Services">
<main class="pt-32 pb-20">

    <header class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12 mb-24">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-error/10 border border-error/20 rounded-full text-error text-xs font-label tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-error animate-pulse"></span>
            Services — Business & IT Consulting
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter font-headline text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                    Strategy <br/><span class="text-primary-fixed-dim">That Hits Home.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg leading-relaxed font-body">
                    Even the best technology fails with the wrong strategy. Our experienced consulting team helps you design a pragmatic digital transformation roadmap that delivers real, measurable ROI.
                </p>
                <div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
                    <a href="/en/contact" class="bg-primary-fixed-dim text-on-primary-fixed px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-headline font-bold hover:brightness-110 transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
                        Free Consultation <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/en/services" class="border border-outline-variant/30 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-headline font-bold hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
                        All Services
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative h-[380px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant/15 bg-surface-container-low flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-fixed-dim/5 to-transparent"></div>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim opacity-20" style="font-size: 200px; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;" data-icon="strategy">strategy</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12 mb-32">
        <div class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Our Consulting Areas</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-fixed-dim to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-5 block" data-icon="map" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">map</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Digital Transformation Roadmap</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">A detailed phased plan for migrating your business operations from conventional systems to an intelligent integrated digital ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-5 block" data-icon="search_insights" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">search_insights</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">IT Infrastructure Audit</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">A comprehensive analysis of your existing technology stack — identifying security gaps, potential failure points, and hidden inefficiencies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-5 block" data-icon="trending_up" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">trending_up</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Automation ROI Quantification</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Before a single line of code is written, we calculate the projected cost savings and productivity gains expected from automation investments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-5 block" data-icon="shield_lock" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">shield_lock</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Data Privacy Compliance Readiness</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Assessment and recommendations to ensure your data infrastructure meets international data privacy laws and Zero Trust security requirements.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-5 block" data-icon="stack" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">stack</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Tech Stack Recommendations</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Selecting the platform, programming language, and architecture most aligned with your business's scale, budget, and long-term objectives.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-5 block" data-icon="groups" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">groups</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Training & Change Management</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">We prepare your team to adopt new technologies with structured training and dedicated support throughout the transition period.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12 mb-32">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-2xl p-12 lg:p-16">
            <div class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Our Consulting Methodology</h2>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-fixed-dim to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-fixed-dim/10 border border-primary-fixed-dim/20 flex items-center justify-center"><span class="font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim text-lg">01</span></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Situation Diagnosis</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">In-depth sessions with key stakeholders to understand real challenges, growth blockers, and the business targets you want to achieve.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-fixed-dim/10 border border-primary-fixed-dim/20 flex items-center justify-center"><span class="font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim text-lg">02</span></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Analysis & Strategy Design</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Comprehensive report covering audit findings, priority recommendations, and a measurable, realistic implementation roadmap.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary-fixed-dim/10 border border-primary-fixed-dim/20 flex items-center justify-center"><span class="font-headline font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim text-lg">03</span></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Execution Accompaniment</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">We don't just deliver reports — we accompany execution, monitor progress, and adjust strategy based on real results in the field.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-fixed-dim/20 to-surface-container-low border border-primary-fixed-dim/20 rounded-2xl p-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Start with a Free Consultation Session</h2>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">60 minutes with our consultants is enough to identify your biggest potential and key roadblocks. Free, no commitment required.</p>
            <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-fixed-dim text-on-primary-fixed px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-headline font-bold hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-fixed-dim/20">
                Schedule Free Session <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="calendar_today">calendar_today</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

</main>
</BaseLayout>
